quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"By the fig, by the olive"
  95,2,by Mount Sinai
  95,3,by this safe town
  95,4,We create man in the finest state
  95,5,then reduce him to the lowest of the low
  95,6,except those who believe and do good deeds––
  95,7,"they will have an unfailing reward. After this, what makes you [man] deny the Judgement"
  95,8,Is God not the most decisive of judges